# Centurion Tor Configuration

# General Tor Settings
SOCKSPort 9050
ControlPort 9051
CookieAuthentication 1
DataDirectory /tmp/tor_centurion

# Logging
Log notice file /tmp/tor_centurion/tor.log
Log warn file /tmp/tor_centurion/tor.log

# Hidden Service for Admin Dashboard
HiddenServiceDir /tmp/tor_centurion/hidden_service/
HiddenServicePort 80 127.0.0.1:8080

# Additional Security
ExitPolicy reject *:*  # No exit relay
SafeLogging 1
